channel.title: Demolitionx, Is back?
channel.description: Hey guys if you can still remember me I quit a while back and contribute to the forums once and a while with an arguable mean post. I have missed playing and running an rsps but most of all coding one. I really would love to code a server with all of you guys again if anyone is interested. I can't even promise it will go out of beta but I really want to put one into beta and code it a bit. I am going to be using a high revision very minimally coded base. If anyone would like to contribute just comment here. Remember this is just for coding, if it does turn out to be a success it will leave beta.
